{"tid":637762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"H股全流通細則發布 投資者先實現減持賣出","createTime":"2018-04-22T06:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T06:28:29.000Z","uid":120541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"17373bdf4cf37ea26f8d71b6c54990ac63fce32d","tid":637762,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"目前有逾200家H股公司是在香港上市的中國境內企業，除建行（939）外，其他公司的內資股股東，均不能在市場減持H股，或將股份抵押融資。但H股全流通後，內資股東便可於市場減持H股或作股份抵押。中國證監會日前表示，已選定聯想控股（3396）為首家全流通試點企業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/h股全流通細則發布-投資者先實現減持賣出-223000504.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fh%E8%82%A1%E5%85%A8%E6%B5%81%E9%80%9A%E7%B4%B0%E5%89%87%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E5%85%88%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E6%B8%9B%E6%8C%81%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA-223000504.html&d=0HwJE49gAfonorBSzpbb2TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3894ecc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/h股全流通細則發布-投資者先實現減持賣出-223000504.html</a><br />\n<br />\n讓領導走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}